This is a system designed for managing and presenting on the web a group of Frequently Asked Questions or FAQs.  Especially if the FAQs are about software products.

It was implemented at Loki Software, Inc. initially by Raf Barrero, and lived as faqs.lokigames.com.

It is being released publicly for the usual reasons and specifically to foster ad-hoc support for the Loki products from the community of users and enthusiasts.

01/24/2002
